Responsibility

Use of SSIL in operational, infrastructure, AI, governance, industrial, financial, or safety-critical contexts is undertaken entirely at the user’s own responsibility.

SSIL provides:

• deterministic irreversibility classification
• bounded horizon evaluation
• explicit continuation governance
• replay-verifiable artifact reproducibility

It does not provide operational authority, regulatory certification, or safety guarantees.


